<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink140">
<l>kāṇmati pāṇanī yuraittaṟ kuriyai</l>
<l>tuṟaikeḻu koṇkaṉ pirinteṉa</l>
<l>viṟaikē ḻelvaḷai nīṅkiya nilaiyē</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
  <l>Look, oh bard; You have the right to narrate</l>
    <l>The state in which the lustrous, luminous bangles have left [my] wrist </l>
      <l>Since the man from the maritime tract that has ghats separatred [from me].</l>
</lg>
    </div>
